A single human figure sitting in deep meditation, dissolving at the edges into countless smaller silhouettes of diverse people that spiral outward like a galaxy, all rendered in warm golden and deep cosmic purple tones. The figure's core remains solid while their outer form fragments and merges with the surrounding crowd of humanity, suggesting unity and interconnection. The background transitions from an intimate, earthy ground into a vast star-filled cosmos, with subtle nebula wisps connecting all the human forms like luminous threads. Studio Ghibli style with soft watercolor textures, dreamlike atmosphere, and gentle luminescent particles floating throughout the scene.
